to get quite complicated. So, we set out to create a way of interacting with R that

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:49.000
gave you a lot of the benefits of the literate programming model and without a lot of the

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:56.160
complication that we have in this. So, this is the interaction model for R notebooks.

